{"tid":1577322,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大埔烏蛟騰抗日烈士紀念碑被塗上「反送中」標語","createTime":"2019-09-17T15:40:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T04:22:12.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"0f203b0751550676adfdc1c7714536779293dd99","tid":1577322,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T15:40:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2019/0917/U634P22T1D785027F1DT20190917185901.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2Fcontent%2F2019%2F0917%2FU634P22T1D785027F1DT20190917185901.jpg&h=1ee63b58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n9月17日，香港唯一一個國家級抗戰紀念設施&mdash;&mdash;烏蛟騰抗日烈士紀念碑多處地方被噴塗上&ldquo;反送中&rdquo;&ldquo;反送中列士&rdquo;等字樣。引起眾多香港市民不滿。<br />\n<br />\n　　烏蛟騰抗日烈士紀念碑是為了紀念東江縱隊港九大隊先烈為抗擊日本侵略者所設。1941年香港淪陷進入三年零八個月的日佔時期，當時廣東人民抗日遊擊隊東江縱隊曾派出精英成立東江縱隊港九大隊，烏蛟騰就是此隊的重要基地。<br />\n<br />\n　　1942年農曆8月16日，日軍包圍烏蛟騰村，強逼村民繳械，並且供出遊擊隊隊員的身分，村長李國藩與多名村民堅拒妥協，終被日軍折磨至死。至香港重光後，村民在烏蛟騰一處山坡豎立紀念碑，緬懷犧牲烈士。後來村民認為該地方太偏僻，遂建議遷至現址。<br />\n<br />\n　　2015年8月，中國國務院公佈《關於公佈第二批國家級抗戰紀念設施、遺址名錄的通知》，當中包括大埔烏蛟騰村烏蛟騰抗日英烈紀念碑。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2019/0917/785027.shtml</code></pre>"},{"pid":"67bc5a21f6bb49196694b5d8b962a2663b51be88","tid":1577322,"uid":231583,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T15:41:09.000Z","msg":"就算自己人做都不割<br />\n但真係點睇都似對家做<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282b8b192d1a5da3faa1880fea7a656fd41a8815","tid":1577322,"uid":82993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T15:42:02.000Z","msg":"呢筆債，佢哋一定要還。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1576589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1576589</a>"},{"pid":"a839fa3bfe5578eeba25f79e03d49e08c55fd266","tid":1577322,"uid":47553,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T15:51:07.000Z","msg":"唔講都唔撚知有d咁嘅嘢<br />\n依家後生嗰d 應該十個有9.5個都未撚聽過有d咁嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n9月仲噴反送中<br />\n做戲都認真d啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d064720d68827e11cf09b9a31cf4261cc269131","tid":1577322,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T15:53:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.sznews.com/news/pic/2019-08/01/aee0cc59-5d44-4348-904b-790df89e43b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sznews.com%2Fnews%2Fpic%2F2019-08%2F01%2Faee0cc59-5d44-4348-904b-790df89e43b9.jpg&h=fb66efa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180818/463806d4b04f4788a810231cba5acafe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20180818%2F463806d4b04f4788a810231cba5acafe.png&h=2e42fc82&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"318927b87d4dbd5b86ece2b47effb66112d979d4","tid":1577322,"uid":62011,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T15:57:43.000Z","msg":"噴都唔噴烏蛟騰啦，咁撚遠。貪佢有蚊阿?"},{"pid":"d5bb5396cbb5fdcf4c472eb098e9626d86bb9b65","tid":1577322,"uid":259973,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T15:59:31.000Z","msg":"聽日組隊的清潔啦，就話係嫁禍，見到好傷心。。。"},{"pid":"06919600a61aa9a67cf5683d8492e8bf2be0e89d","tid":1577322,"uid":77788,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T15:59:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7dc8749c944bee97f889f689585a6d215b58caf3","tid":1577322,"uid":120757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:02:26.000Z","msg":"冇人識wor"},{"pid":"05dd97ac2946b79c008f88b7c596f673f064e9a3","tid":1577322,"uid":23649,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"06919600a61aa9a67cf5683d8492e8bf2be0e89d","tid":1577322,"uid":77788,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T15:59:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime"